name: Karakuri Toad Oil
desc: Activate this card by targeting 1 “Karakuri” monster in your GY; Special Summon it, and if you do, equip this card to it. Once per turn, if the battle position of a face-up “Karakuri” monster you control is changed: The equipped monster gains 500 ATK/DEF. You can only activate 1 "Karakuri Toad Oil" once per turn.
